<p><b>How much does the ITIL exam cost?</b> ITIL Exam cost For those who prefer self-study, you can use the available resources to prepare for the ITIL exam then book your test directly through PeopleCert for $680 to $865 per test. The practitioner-level exams cost $280 per test. All of the ITIL exams are proctored tests administered by PeopleCert.</p>
<p><b>What is the passing score for the ITIL exam?</b> The ITIL® Foundation exam consists of 40 multiple-choice questions that must be completed within 60 minutes. To pass, you need to score at least 65% (26 out of 40 questions). Many candidates opt for self-paced online courses or study guides to achieve this.</p>
<p><b>Is ITIL certification worth IT?</b> Distinguishing Factor in the Job Market: In the competitive field of IT, having an ITIL certification can set you apart from other candidates. It signals to potential employers that you thoroughly understand IT service management principles and practices, making you a valuable asset to any team.</p>
<p><b>How long is ITIL 4 certification good for?</b> When do I have to renew my ITIL certification? Candidates have to update their ITIL certification within three years from the issue date.</p>
